track.name: Section I
comments: it was my first encounter with serial music back then, beautifull
I hope Stuart is right. Whether he is or not this is a wonderful piece of music.
I LOVE the timbre produced by the violin and cello sections in this movement. It sounds like a piece of industrial machinery.

I think that assumption is a bit far to go.

But it's nice to listen to, that's about as far as it needs to go sometimes.

new age in deed and we have been waiting for a change for the better for a very, very long time. Maybe this is the early signal that the world humanity will transform itself to a higher level of enlightenment and elevate our existence to  the more important issues which have been ignored
